 Part 2: Crime Analysis Algorithms
1. Repeat Offender & Behavioral Pattern Analysis â€“ Identifies repeat criminals and behavioral trends.
2. Spatiotemporal Crime Prediction (Time-Series Analysis) â€“ Predicts crime trends over time and location.
3. DBSCAN (Density-Based Spatial Clustering) â€“ Detects crime hotspots through clustering.
4. K-Means Clustering Algorithm â€“ Segments crime-prone areas based on geographical data.

